Package org.photonlib.examples.simposeest.robot

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutoController
    Implements logic to convert a set of desired waypoints (ie, a trajectory) and the current estimate of where the robot is at (ie, the estimated Pose) into motion commands for a drivetrain.
    Constants
    Holding class for all physical constants that must be used throughout the codebase.
    Drivetrain
    Implements a controller for the drivetrain.
    DrivetrainPoseEstimator
    Performs estimation of the drivetrain's current position on the field, using a vision system, drivetrain encoders, and a gyroscope.
    OperatorInterface  
    PoseTelemetry
    Reports our expected, desired, and actual poses to dashboards
    Robot
